<div class="top-bar">
  <div class="top-bar-inner">
    <a href="/" class="top-bar-brand">Linchpin Realty</a>
    <div class="top-bar-links">
      <a href="#">Portfolio</a>
      <a href="#">Loans</a>
      <a href="#">Investors</a>
      <a href="#">Settings</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-wide">

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── HERO ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section" style="padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 4rem;">
    <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Style Guide</p>
    <h1 class="heading-display">Linchpin Realty</h1>
    <p class="text-body" style="max-width: 36rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
      Visual language reference for the LPR platform. Hard money lending,
      real estate investment, portfolio management &mdash; built for clarity and speed.
    </p>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── TYPOGRAPHY ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Typography</span>

    <div style="display: grid; gap: 2rem;">
      <div style="max-width: 42rem;">
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.heading-display &middot; Barlow Condensed &middot; 3.5rem / 800 &middot; uppercase</p>
        <p class="heading-display">$4.2M Funded This Quarter</p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
          The quarterly origination target was exceeded by 18%, driven by a surge
          in bridge loan applications across Brooklyn and Queens. Three deals over
          $1M closed in the final two weeks alone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 42rem;">
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.heading-1 &middot; Barlow Condensed &middot; 2.5rem / 700 &middot; uppercase</p>
        <p class="heading-1">Portfolio Overview</p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
          Forty-seven active loans totaling $18.4M across the five boroughs. The
          weighted average interest rate sits at 14.2% with an average term of
          fourteen months. Delinquency rate remains below 3%.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 42rem;">
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.heading-2 &middot; Barlow Condensed &middot; 1.75rem / 700 &middot; uppercase</p>
        <p class="heading-2">Active Loan Pipeline</p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Twelve applications are currently in underwriting, representing $4.8M in
          potential originations. Six are rehab projects, four are bridge loans,
          and two are ground-up construction.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 42rem;">
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.heading-3 &middot; Barlow Condensed &middot; 1.25rem / 600 &middot; mixed case</p>
        <p class="heading-3">Borrower Details</p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Anthony Marchetti, operating through Marchetti Holdings LLC, has completed
          three prior loans with Linchpin. All were repaid on or ahead of schedule.
          Current request is for a 12-unit conversion in Astoria.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 42rem;">
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.heading-4 &middot; Barlow Condensed &middot; 1rem / 600 &middot; mixed case</p>
        <p class="heading-4">Property Address</p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          37-12 31st Avenue, Astoria, NY 11103. Zoned R6B, currently configured as
          a six-unit walk-up with ground-floor retail. Proposed scope includes full
          gut renovation and conversion to twelve residential units.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 42rem;">
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.text-body &middot; System Sans &middot; 1rem / 400 &middot; 1.75 line-height</p>
        <p class="text-body">
          Linchpin Realty provides short-term bridge loans and hard money financing
          for real estate investors and developers across the New York metro area.
          We move fast, underwrite smart, and close deals others won't touch.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.text-small &middot; System Sans &middot; 0.875rem / 400</p>
        <p class="text-small">Last updated March 6, 2026 &middot; All figures in USD</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.text-mono &middot; IBM Plex Mono &middot; 0.875rem / 400</p>
        <p class="text-mono">LOAN-2026-0042 &middot; 12.5% &middot; 18mo &middot; $1,250,000</p>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">UI Elements</p>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem;">
        <div>
          <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.section-label &middot; Barlow Condensed &middot; 11px / 600 &middot; uppercase</p>
          <p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 0;">Example Section Label</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">.stat-value &middot; Barlow Condensed &middot; 2rem / 800</p>
          <p class="stat-value">$4,200,000</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Field label &middot; Barlow Condensed &middot; 0.8125rem / 600 &middot; uppercase</p>
          <div class="field" style="margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0.25rem;">
            <label style="margin-bottom: 0;">Borrower Name</label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── COLORS ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Colors</span>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(120px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem;">
      <div>
        <div style="height: 64px; border-radius: 6px; background: #000000;"></div>
        <p class="text-mono" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Black</p>
        <p class="text-small">#000000</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="height: 64px; border-radius: 6px; background: #1a1a1a;"></div>
        <p class="text-mono" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Soot</p>
        <p class="text-small">#1a1a1a</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="height: 64px; border-radius: 6px; background: #031d55;"></div>
        <p class="text-mono" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Navy</p>
        <p class="text-small">#031d55</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="height: 64px; border-radius: 6px; background: #8a8f9a;"></div>
        <p class="text-mono" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Steel</p>
        <p class="text-small">#8a8f9a</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="height: 64px; border-radius: 6px; background: #c4c7cc;"></div>
        <p class="text-mono" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Concrete</p>
        <p class="text-small">#c4c7cc</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="height: 64px; border-radius: 6px; background: #f4f5f6; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"></div>
        <p class="text-mono" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Smoke</p>
        <p class="text-small">#f4f5f6</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="height: 64px; border-radius: 6px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"></div>
        <p class="text-mono" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">White</p>
        <p class="text-small">#ffffff</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="section-label" style="margin-top: 3rem;">Secondary / Status Colors</p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: #3d5575;"></div>
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: #678097;"></div>
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(103, 128, 151, 0.1); border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-mono">Slate Blue</p>
        <p class="text-small">#678097 (dark: #3d5575) &middot; Success, notifications, button hovers</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: #725a24;"></div>
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: #8a6d2b;"></div>
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(138, 109, 43, 0.1); border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-mono">Caution</p>
        <p class="text-small">#8a6d2b &middot; Warnings, past due, attention needed</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: #3d1212;"></div>
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: #571a1a;"></div>
          <div style="height: 48px; flex: 1; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(107, 32, 32, 0.08); border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-mono">Maroon</p>
        <p class="text-small">#571a1a &middot; Danger, defaults, destructive actions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── BUTTONS ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Buttons &mdash; Corner Bracket</span>
    <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Barlow Condensed &middot; 13px / 600 &middot; 0.14em tracking &middot; uppercase</p>
    <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Corners expand to full border on hover. Use <code class="text-mono">btn_tag</code> helper or add <code class="text-mono">.corners-t</code> / <code class="text-mono">.corners-b</code> spans.</p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.5rem; overflow: hidden;">
      <%# light background %>
      <div style="background: var(--color-smoke); padding: 3rem 3.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <span class="text-mono" style="font-size: 10px; color: var(--color-concrete); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Light</span>
        <%= btn_tag "Schedule a Call", "#" %>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
          <%= btn_tag "Small", "#", class: "btn-sm" %>
          <%= btn_tag "Default", "#" %>
          <%= btn_tag "Large", "#", class: "btn-lg" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# dark background %>
      <div class="ctx-dark" style="background: var(--color-soot); padding: 3rem 3.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start;">
        <span class="text-mono" style="font-size: 10px; color: #383838; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Dark</span>
        <%= btn_tag "Schedule a Call", "#" %>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
          <%= btn_tag "Small", "#", class: "btn-sm" %>
          <%= btn_tag "Default", "#" %>
          <%= btn_tag "Large", "#", class: "btn-lg" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# black background %>
      <div class="ctx-black" style="background: #000; padding: 3rem 3.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; border-right: 1px solid #252525; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <span class="text-mono" style="font-size: 10px; color: #383838; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Black</span>
        <%= btn_tag "Request a Proposal", "#" %>
      </div>

      <%# navy background %>
      <div class="ctx-navy" style="background: var(--color-navy); padding: 3rem 3.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <span class="text-mono" style="font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Navy</span>
        <%= btn_tag "Get Financing", "#" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="section-label" style="margin-top: 3rem;">Filled Buttons (forms, destructive actions)</p>
    <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Use <code class="text-mono">btn_filled_tag</code> helper. Variants: <code class="text-mono">primary</code>, <code class="text-mono">danger</code>, <code class="text-mono">ghost</code>.</p>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
      <%= btn_filled_tag "Submit Inquiry", "#", variant: "primary" %>
      <%= btn_filled_tag "Confirm Default", "#", variant: "danger" %>
      <%= btn_filled_tag "Cancel", "#", variant: "ghost" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── BADGES ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Badges</span>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center;">
      <span class="badge badge-navy">Funded</span>
      <span class="badge badge-success">Performing</span>
      <span class="badge badge-warning">Past Due</span>
      <span class="badge badge-danger">Default</span>
      <span class="badge badge-neutral">Draft</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── STAT BLOCKS ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Stats</span>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="stat-value">$18.4M</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Total Funded</div>
        <div class="stat-change-up" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">+12.3% vs last quarter</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="stat-value">47</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Active Loans</div>
        <div class="stat-change-up" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">+8 this month</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="stat-value">14.2%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Avg. Interest Rate</div>
        <div class="stat-change-down" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">-0.4% vs last quarter</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="stat-value">$392K</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Avg. Loan Size</div>
        <div class="stat-label" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Steady</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── CARDS ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Cards</span>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div class="card">
        <p class="heading-4">Standard Card</p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Default card with border. Good for general content containers,
          form sections, and data groupings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-elevated">
        <p class="heading-4">Elevated Card</p>
        <p class="text-body" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Shadow variant for featured content, modals, and primary
          action areas that need visual lift.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-dark">
        <p class="heading-4" style="color: white;">Dark Card</p>
        <p style="color: #8a8f9a; margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.625;">
          For high-contrast sections, CTAs, and featured metrics.
          Pairs well with white stat values.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-navy" style="grid-column: span 2;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;">
          <div>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-weight: 600;">Featured Investment</p>
            <p class="heading-2" style="color: white; margin-top: 0.25rem;">142-08 Queens Blvd, Jamaica</p>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem;">
              Mixed-use &middot; 12 units &middot; Bridge loan &middot; 18 months
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align: right;">
            <div style="color: white; font-size: 1.875rem; font-weight: 800;">$2.1M</div>
            <div style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;">Loan Amount</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-small" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Quick Action</p>
        <p class="heading-3">New Loan Application</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 1rem;"><%= btn_tag "Start Application", "#" %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── CHARTS (React) ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Charts (React Components)</span>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem;">
      <div class="card">
        <%= react_component("BarChart", {
          title: "Monthly Originations ($K)",
          data: [
            { label: "Sep", value: 840 },
            { label: "Oct", value: 1120 },
            { label: "Nov", value: 960 },
            { label: "Dec", value: 1340 },
            { label: "Jan", value: 1580 },
            { label: "Feb", value: 1210 }
          ]
        }) %>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <%= react_component("DonutChart", {
          title: "Portfolio by Property Type",
          data: [
            { label: "Multi-Family", value: 42 },
            { label: "Mixed-Use", value: 28 },
            { label: "Commercial", value: 18 },
            { label: "Single-Family", value: 12 }
          ]
        }) %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── TABLE ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Tables</span>

    <div class="card" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden;">
      <div style="padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0;">
        <p class="heading-3">Recent Loans</p>
      </div>
      <div class="table-container" style="padding: 1rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;">
        <table class="data-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Loan ID</th>
              <th>Borrower</th>
              <th>Property</th>
              <th>Amount</th>
              <th>Rate</th>
              <th>Term</th>
              <th>Status</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-mono">LPR-2026-0042</td>
              <td>Anthony Marchetti</td>
              <td>37-12 31st Ave, Astoria</td>
              <td class="text-money">$1,250,000</td>
              <td>13.5%</td>
              <td>18 mo</td>
              <td><span class="badge badge-success">Performing</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-mono">LPR-2026-0041</td>
              <td>Greenline Capital LLC</td>
              <td>88-01 Queens Blvd, Elmhurst</td>
              <td class="text-money">$2,100,000</td>
              <td>14.0%</td>
              <td>12 mo</td>
              <td><span class="badge badge-navy">Funded</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-mono">LPR-2026-0039</td>
              <td>David Kim</td>
              <td>104-20 Atlantic Ave, Ozone Park</td>
              <td class="text-money">$680,000</td>
              <td>12.0%</td>
              <td>24 mo</td>
              <td><span class="badge badge-warning">Past Due</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-mono">LPR-2026-0038</td>
              <td>Summit Holdings Inc</td>
              <td>215 W 125th St, Harlem</td>
              <td class="text-money">$3,400,000</td>
              <td>15.0%</td>
              <td>6 mo</td>
              <td><span class="badge badge-success">Performing</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="text-mono">LPR-2026-0035</td>
              <td>Maria Santos</td>
              <td>58-19 Woodside Ave, Woodside</td>
              <td class="text-money">$420,000</td>
              <td>13.0%</td>
              <td>12 mo</td>
              <td><span class="badge badge-neutral">Draft</span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── FORMS ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Forms</span>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem;">
      <div class="card">
        <p class="heading-3" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Loan Inquiry</p>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="borrower_name">Borrower Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="borrower_name" class="field-input" placeholder="Full legal name">
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="loan_amount">Loan Amount</label>
          <input type="text" id="loan_amount" class="field-input" placeholder="$0.00">
          <p class="field-hint">Minimum $100,000</p>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="property_type">Property Type</label>
          <select id="property_type" class="field-input">
            <option value="">Select type...</option>
            <option>Multi-Family</option>
            <option>Mixed-Use</option>
            <option>Commercial</option>
            <option>Single-Family</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="property_address">Property Address</label>
          <input type="text" id="property_address" class="field-input" placeholder="Street, City, State, ZIP">
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="notes">Notes</label>
          <textarea id="notes" class="field-input" placeholder="Exit strategy, rehab scope, etc."></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="form-actions">
          <%= btn_filled_tag "Submit Inquiry", "#", variant: "primary" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <p class="heading-4" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Field States</p>

          <div class="field">
            <label>Default</label>
            <input type="text" class="field-input" placeholder="Placeholder text">
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label>With Value</label>
            <input type="text" class="field-input" value="142-08 Queens Blvd">
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label>With Error</label>
            <input type="text" class="field-input" style="border-color: #571a1a;" value="">
            <p class="field-error">This field is required</p>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label>Disabled</label>
            <input type="text" class="field-input" value="Read-only value" disabled style="opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed;">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <p class="heading-4" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Inline Confirmation</p>
          <p class="text-body" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Are you sure you want to mark this loan as defaulted?</p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem;">
            <%= btn_filled_tag "Confirm Default", "#", variant: "danger" %>
            <%= btn_filled_tag "Cancel", "#", variant: "ghost" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── FLASH MESSAGES ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Flash Messages</span>

    <div style="display: grid; gap: 1rem; max-width: 36rem;">
      <div class="flash-notice">Loan LPR-2026-0042 has been funded successfully.</div>
      <div class="flash-alert">Payment overdue. Contact borrower immediately.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── DARK SECTION ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div class="section" style="background: #000; margin-left: -1.5rem; margin-right: -1.5rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem; border-top: none;">
    <span class="section-label" style="color: #8a8f9a;">Dark Context</span>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start;">
      <div>
        <p class="heading-1" style="color: white;">Built for<br>the boroughs.</p>
        <p style="color: #8a8f9a; margin-top: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.875rem;">
          Linchpin Realty was born in Queens and built for the five boroughs.
          We understand the deals, the neighborhoods, and the hustle it takes
          to build something real.
        </p>
        <div class="ctx-black" style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
          <%= btn_tag "Get Started", "#" %>
          <%= btn_tag "Learn More", "#" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem;">
        <div class="card-dark" style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
          <div class="stat-value" style="color: white;">$82M</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">Lifetime Funded</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-dark" style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
          <div class="stat-value" style="color: white;">340+</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">Loans Closed</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-dark" style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
          <div class="stat-value" style="color: white;">98%</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">Repayment Rate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-dark" style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
          <div class="stat-value" style="color: white;">4 Days</div>
          <div class="stat-label" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">Avg. Close Time</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ──────────────────────────────── FOOTER SPACER ──────────────────────────────── %>
  <div style="padding: 4rem 0;"></div>
</div>
